show.title: Deadly Temptation
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/Q4xRWV
show.description: It's the story of a young woman from a rural village — innocent at heart, free from deceit or malice. Armed only with her talent earned through sheer hard work, she arrives in the city in search of her future groom. What unfolds is a delightful journey filled with humorous and heartwarming experiences. With plenty of moments to make you smile, this charming series is sure to win your heart.
